title: Book Of Catta
author: Cattus_
pages:
#- In the name of Catta, the merciful, the compassionate.

Praise be to Catta, Lord of this world. Master of all of Civcraft. 

Guide me in the path of your will, Catta.

Catta's prayer.
#- Catism is made up of 5 cores all followers must follow to call themselves Catist.
1. Peace
2. Altruism
3. Zacat.
4. Forgiveness
5. Loyalty to Catta.

The Five cores will be
explained later. 
#- Just What is Catism?

Catism is the belief that Catta is the Lord of Civcraft and it's creator and Cattus_
is his prophet. Catist believe that humankind has been corrupted by greed and hate. Catist attempt to remove greed and hate by speading Catism. 
#- Once all follow the five cores Civcraft will reach a end game utopia. 

So do you guys like worship cats lol?

In a way yes. Catta the creator, is a Cat and all Cats are made in his image. Cats were made before humankind. 
#- The Cats have been corrupted by the negative qualities Catta gave humans. Corrupted Cats are known as Ocelots. Ocelots can be made pure and holy again by feeding holy fish. Holy fish is fish that has been cleaned and blessed in a Catist temple.
#- Why did Catta give humans negative qualities? Why doesn't he just change Cats back to normal as well?

Catta gave humans negative qualities like hate and greed to keep from getting to powerful, but instead the negative qualities
took over and made
#- the world full of suffering we have today. Catta doesn't want to see in this sad state and sent Cattus_ to spread his will that will slove all suffering. Catta would have fixed the suffering of the world, but because he gave humankind total freewill, 
#- humankind will have to fix the world them selves. 
The Holy Cats can't be changed back because becoming one with Catta is a personal journey that must be done within oneself.
#-      The Five Cores
     Of Catism.
1. Peace.
 Catta created us all equally so to wage war or murder others is wrong. However, the Catist must be ready to defend himself from the corrupted. The corrupted of course those controlled by negative qualities. 
#- 2. Altruism.
The Catist must care about those around them and their community. Selfishness is a quality of the corrupted, not the Catist. Hoarding large amounts of wealth is slefish. Catists must care for all their brothers and sisters, even if they 
#- Are not Catist.
#- 3. Zacat.
Zacat is the act of giving to those around the Catist, including the less fortunate. Zacat is not a special date, but rather lasts all year. It is very important for a Catist to practice Zacat.
#- 4. Forgiveness
Catist must be willing to extend the paw of forgiveness to all those who accept it. If someone has wronged the Catist the Catist must forgive them. If the wrong do-er rejects the paw of forgiveness and attacks the Catist, the Catist must 
#- defend themselves. Self defense is always allowed. 
#- 5. Loyalty To Catta.
Catta calls for loyalty to himself and for all to follow his will. It is important to note that Catta does not punish those who disobey him. Catta gave humankind free will. Catta wants to see the best for human kind and has thus given
#- humans a plan for a utopian world, and they are know as the five cores of Catism.
#-   The Rose is the perfect metaphor for Catism.

The green stem is the path to living a non-corrupted lifestyle. On the stem are thorns. The thorns are the corrupted and those who will try to stray you from reaching the Flower.
#- The flower or red part of the rose is a non-corrupted lifestyle. One must travel down the stem and overcome the thorns to reach the flower. 
#- Want to be a Catist? Great, just follow Catta and the five cores and build a temple in your local community. One does not have to ask to be a Catist. 
If you would like like to reach other Catist msg Cattuscat on reddit or Cattus_ in game. 
#- 